### TreeShell Commands

- `""` (empty) - Show current menu/options
- `jump X.Y.Z` - Navigate to specific coordinate
- `back` - Go back to previous position  
- `menu` - Show current node menu
- `NUMBER` - Execute numbered menu option
- `NUMBER {"key": "value"}` - Execute with arguments

